 and s_nationkey = n_nationkey
 and n_name = \'GERMANY\'

 ( select sum(ps_supplycost * ps_availqty) * 0.00001000000
 
 
 from partsupp,
 supplier,
 nation
 where ps_suppkey = s_suppkey
 and s_nationkey = n_nationkey
 and n_name = \'GERMANY\'
 )
order by value desc;":str, "default_pipe":str, 140:int);
